Katie Sheridan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katie_Sheridan 0 Katie Teresa Sheridan is an English actress who became known for her role as Sophie Norton in the Nickelodeon comedy series Genie in the House. Her television roles also include appearances in the BBC series Doctors, Waking the Dead and Lovesoup. In 2015 Sheridan created and starred in her own online series, romantic comedy Match Not Found. She was nominated for Best Lead Actor in a web series at the Raindance Film Festival 2016 for this role. The series is currently releasing its third season and has been announced as a finalist in the C21 Drama Awards.
